column2: select p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.deVRad_r, p.u, p.r, p.extinction_r, p.extinction_u, s.z as RedShift from galaxy p, dbo.fgetNearByObjEq(#,#,#) n, galSpecInfo s where p.objid=n.objid and p.specObjID=s.specObjID and p.specObjID<># and s.z between # and # and s.zWarning = # order by s.z desc
